   ["Reduces the cooldown of your Hammer of Justice by 10 sec, increases the duration of your Seal of Justice effect by 1 sec and your Judgement spells also reduce the melee attack speed of the target by 20%."] = "Hammer of Justice'in bekleme süresini 10 sn azaltır, Seal of Justice etkinin süresini 1 sn artırır ve Judgement büyülerin ayrıca hedefin yakın dövüş saldırı hızını %20 azaltır.",
