   ["Reduces the cooldown of your Inner Focus, Power Infusion, Pain Suppression and Penance spells by 10%."] = "Inner Focus, Power Infusion, Pain Suppression ve Penance büyülerinin bekleme süresini %10 azaltır.",
   ["Reduces the cooldown of your Inner Focus, Power Infusion, Pain Suppression and Penance spells by 20%."] = "Inner Focus, Power Infusion, Pain Suppression ve Penance büyülerinin bekleme süresini %20 azaltır.",
